title: 加了CoFH Core后游戏加载失败
txt_content:
萌新游戏又加载失败了原因就是加了CoFH Core
求大佬们解答







fml-client-latest.log


2019-12-23 18:09 上传
点击文件名下载附件




156.52 KB, 下载次数: 8

replies.author: ItIsEnderman
replies.txt_content:
[18:06:30] [Client thread/ERROR] [FML/]: The mod ThermalDynamics (Thermal Dynamics) requires mods [CoFHCore] to be available


这不是没安装吗，重发一下日志

replies.author: a1294790523
replies.txt_content:
[18:06:29] [Client thread/DEBUG] [FML/]: No mcmod.info file found in directory 3H31.7.10CoFHCore3.0.0RC7-211mod
你这装的什么玩意....
https://www.curseforge.com/minec ... -core/files/2388750
删除掉然后在这里下一个吧（

replies.author: paperspigot
replies.txt_content: 提示: 作者被禁止或删除 内容自动屏蔽
